Using Plexus in your applications

<<This is an old piece of documentation, yet to be integrated into the new site and removed>>

If you want to use plexus as a part of the larger application then you should read about [Plexus Embedder].
* If you want to embed plexus in web container then you might want to use goodies provided by [Plexus servlet] project
* If you want to use plexus for running your application then use [plexus runtime builder]

